title: marginal (infra-party) changes toward decency
pid: 7762d892-a7d6-4596-9050-949a308f01f5
body: |2-
  I wish I had suggested to some Colombian political candidate
  a platform whereby they promised
  the same level of state violence as Abelardo
  but promised to respect human rights in the process.
  Who could want what Abelardo promised and not prefer that?
